    "Lastly, when comparing the median over all scenarios, the MARL algorithm dominated in 78% of the cases.",
    "In this work, a multi-agent reinforcement learning approach for online layout planning and scheduling in line-less mobile assembly systems trained using a discrete event simulation was presented.",
    "The main contribution was a LMAS control algorithm implementing operational flexibility and an openfield layout with movable facilities.",
    "The approach was able to adapt to changing conditions and effectively coordinate multiple jobs and stations within an assembly system to achieve the overall goal of minimizing the makespan.",
